        .container

            .row.align-items-center.justify-content-center

                .col-lg-6
                    .badge.badge-primary-soft.text-primary.badge-marketing.badge-pill.mb-3 Get Started!
                    .mb-5
                        h2 Research the right way
                        p.lead
                            | 70% of researchers get overwhelmed when performing desk research. Scrutiny nudges your research in the right direction and speeds up knowledge discovery time by 80%
                    .row
                        .col-md-6.mb-4
                            h6 Search
                            p.mb-2.small Search over 300 million literature documents including top journals, conferences and patents
                        .col-md-6.mb-4
                            h6 Swipe
                            p.mb-2.small.mb-0 We only show you the relevant information, if you think a document is useful simply swipe right!

                    .row
                        .col-md-6.mb-4
                            h6 Store
                            p.mb-2.small.mb-0 Don't waste time organising your documents, all searches are pre-sorted so you can spend more time creating impact through your work

                        .col-md-6.mb-4
                            h6 Share
                            p.small.mb-0 Easily share documents between devices, colleagues, research associates and more through scrutiny web
                            a.small.text-arrow-icon(href="https://web.scrutiny.app/")
                                | Access Now!
                                i(data-feather="arrow-right")
                .col-lg-6.z-1(data-aos='fade-left')
